data.description: Country living in the city in BOAT TOWN USA! Nice bungalow on .46 acres of property. Close to I-94, Lake St. Clair marinas, grocery shopping, schools, and close to several delicious "mom and pop" restaurants! Fenced yard completed 4 years ago for ultimate privacy. Large primary bedroom on 2nd floor. Second bedroom on main floor. Bonus/sitting room on main floor. Detached 2-car garage and a shed. Nice sized kitchen and living room. Sun-room off the back of the house. This home is move-in ready!  Hurry and see this great opportunity!
